	Metrics presented measure each investment product based on (i) rank above the median of its peer category within Morningstar (mutual funds) or eVestment (institutional composites) for unconstrained and fully-active investment products; or (ii) outperformance against its benchmark index for "index like", rules based, risk-constrained, or client-specific investment products. Fixed Income excludes Senior Bank Loan assets. Senior Bank Loan includes mutual funds, institutional collective trusts and institutional advisory.


                                        














